  "ciliary_role": "SNX17 functions in early stages of ciliogenesis. Regulates the homeostasis of centriolar satellite proteins including PCM1, CEP131, and OFD1 during serum starvation induced ciliogenesis. Recruits USP9X to antagonise MIB1-induced degradation of PCM1, maintaining the integrity of centriolar satellites. SNX17 deficiency leads degradation of USP9X and PCM1, and disrupts ciliogenesis upon serum starvation (31671755).",
